[{"ec":"ET00000849","t":"Hero (1983)","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/hero-1983-et00000849-1753697954.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/hero-1983-et00000849-1753697954.jpg","d":"The film starts off with Pasha (Amrish Puri) being taken to prison. To get out of the situation, he writes to his best man, Jackie (Jackie Shroff), who goes and warns Shrikanth Mathur (Shammi Kapoor). He then kidnaps Shrikanth`s daughter Radha (Meenakshi Sheshadri) and tells her that he is a police officer. They eventualy fall in love; however, later she finds out that he is a goon. Nevertheless, she does not leave him but urges him to surrender. Transformed by true love, Jackie surrenders himself to the police and is imprisoned for two years. But, nobody from Radha`s family accepts their relationship, and set up a series of hurdles. Will Radha and Jackie`s love pass the test of time?","rd":"1983-02-26","rt":173,"ct":"U","g":["Drama","Musical","Romantic"],"l":["Hindi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Jackie Shroff","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/jackie-shroff-882-19-09-2017-05-13-08.jpg"],["Meenakshi Seshadri","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/meenakshi-seshadri-4958-20-11-2017-01-00-28.jpg"],["Sanjeev Kumar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/sanjeev-kumar-5227-1765365340.jpg"],["Amrish Puri","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/amrish-puri-4574-24-03-2017-17-31-53.jpg"],["Shammi Kapoor","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/shammi-kapoor-5226-02-06-2017-17-10-36.jpg"],["Madan Puri","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/madan-puri-iein003466-24-03-2017-12-50-37.jpg"],["Shakti Kapoor","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/shakti-kapoor-2100-24-03-2017-12-33-30.jpg"]]